{"tid":1242443,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"同事表現差冇花紅收 竟敢第二日遞辭職信","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:43:38.000Z","uid":196627,"like":1,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a18e7a7a55e9cde6ded1f5747bf2fbc16eb3ba7","tid":1242443,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n前幾日我公司就派花紅喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有幾個同事學野慢<br />\n份人又蠢<br />\n咁我身為公司高層-人力資源主仼<br />\n梗係唔派花紅比佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來諗住呢<br />\n佢地會反省下自己既工作態度<br />\n但佢地唔反省啦不特止<br />\n仲喺同一日向我遞埋信辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到好似我公司唔派花紅比佢地係我問題咁<br />\n我公司唔炒佢地都算係咁<br />\n仲要用呢一種態度回應我地公司<br />\n諗番起真係愈來愈嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有出reference letter嗰時<br />\n儘量寫得衰D<br />\n等佢地搵唔到其他工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a880e8a32e614f13744018a727e93697e975595c","tid":1242443,"uid":196627,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"我個post完全唔係for笑<br />\n公司目的係利潤最大化<br />\n目的係警惕所有應徵者<br />\n幫大部分幼稚連登仔建立正確工作價值觀<br />\n要笑既可以正評後出翻去"},{"pid":"493e6a54c752dc41820e9c77d7f9d6cc576f2f18","tid":1242443,"uid":136038,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"樓主假膠唔洗理"},{"pid":"e9d94ea2e15b9ded1372b9ba70b33313911dedd0","tid":1242443,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"fumgaying add oil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我追蹤咗你, 事隔四五個月先出山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aad7f9cef8e54bb6e82980702f35c13ef7c